{
  "stem": "22734.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were allowed to go out, walk on-- up and down the Lagerstrasse, as they call it, I don't know, for sometime during the day.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But certainly you were-- you were supposed to look busy, like carry something from here to there so that they don't attack you that you are working.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was no work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was-- you-- people carried stone from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was nothing to work on, but-- yet you were supposedly working.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it-- it was empty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no-- there was no tier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were little-- the-- the men in the-- in the-- there was a work shop.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they made them little tables and little stools.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and they played with woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, from this Kommando Kanada, they brought some toys, they-- the way they brought toy-- they brought books, and they brought coloring books, and pencils.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And slowly, but we had stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not much, but we had a little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then when it got nice, we would play-- we would play outside, which was almost at the wire, because it was already March and it was-- this was later.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was April and it was May.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was getting warmer and the mud was getting muddier, because whatever frost there was, it defrosted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was-- it was easier to be outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It wasn't so cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It wasn't so bitter cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The sun sometimes shone-- shining.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it helped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you saw the selections.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, you-- it was like a big theater.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because we were right behind the railway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was the wire, and there was a piece of no man's land, And then there was the rail and the platform.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So you saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
